John Ewart https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/John_Ewart 0 John Ewart (26 February 1928 – 8 March 1994) was an Australian actor of radio, stage, television and film. Ewart won an AACTA Award for Best Actor in a Supporting Role. He was married to children's host Jane Fennell.
